# wiki/queries/

LLM Chat 中的**优秀回答归档**。

[[Karpathy]] 原文："good answers can be filed back into the wiki as new pages. A comparison you asked for, an analysis, a connection you discovered — these are valuable and shouldn't disappear into chat history."

**命名约定**：`<short-title>.md`

**页面类型**：`type: Query`（详见 [[schema.md]] §3.7）

**作用**：让 [[探索性提问]] 也能复利累积，而非淹没在 chat history 中。
